oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: Grand Ole Opry stars Jim & Jesse at Frontier City
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:subject: Grand ole opry (Radio program); Jim and Jesse; Homesteaders (Musical group); Drake, Pete; Campbell, Archie, 1914-1987;
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: Three color half sheet (black and red on yellow) announcing the Grand Ole Opry stars Jim and Jesse with the Virginia Boys, the Homesteaders, Pete Drake, Archie Campbell, and Bobby Smith at the Frontier City on July 17. Poster features metal photoplates of Jim and Jesse, Pete Drake, the Homesteaders and Archie Campbell.
